properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 29 at 8:03PM EST until January 31 at 5:00AM EST by NWS Jacksonville FL
properties.description:
* WHAT...North northeast winds 25 to 30 knots with occasional
gusts to gale force expected. Seas 7 to 10 feet with
occasional seas up to 13 feet.

* WHERE...Waters from St. Augustine to Flagler Beach FL from 20
to 60 NM.

* WHEN...From 1 AM Thursday to 5 AM EST Friday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 1 AM THURSDAY TO 5 AM EST FRIDAY
